    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wooden or bamboo structures attached to the back with a carrying strap connected to a front band. Used to transport goods in Mexico.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
